---
title: Roasted Sweet Potato Farro Bowls with Marinated Cranberries & Pepitas
description: Farro, a variety of hulled wheat, is praised for its chewy texture and nutty flavor. To make this grain bowl shine, we pair our beloved farro with roasted vegetables, fresh watercress, sweet-tart marinated cranberries, lemony dressing, nutty Parmesan, and crunchy pepitas. You’re not farro from digging into this hearty meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/roasted-sweet-potato-farro-bowls-55e07a66.jpg
